            "title": "Kenall Lighting introduces new patient room lighting - MedMaster Pillow™ and Pillow™ Slot luminaires. Aiming for patient comfort, it sets a new benchmark.",
            "id": "2f48ac02-b1ff-442f-86d2-06c22c4beeec",
            "description": "In a recent announcement on January 14, 2026, in Kenosha, Wisconsin, Kenall Lighting introduced the MedMaster Pillow™ and Pillow™ Slot luminaires. These innovative lighting fixtures aim to enhance patient room comfort and care by setting a new standard in design. The Pillow family of luminaires features gentle curves and a soothing over-bed appearance to create a calming atmosphere. These fixtures provide cove-like illumination, representing a significant advancement in healthcare lighting solutions. This launch signifies Kenall Lighting's dedication to improving patient experiences, with the aim of positively impacting healthcare environments. The introduction of the MedMaster Pillow™ and Pillow™ Slot luminaires marks a milestone in the industry's commitment to enhancing patient well-being.",
